&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Arteria AI&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arteria AI is the agentic backbone of financial services operations. We build AI-powered tools that help tier-one global institutions manage their most complex document workflows faster, smarter, and at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We were founded by lawyers and financial services practitioners who have spent 20+ years solving documentation problems with the world&#39;s largest companies. Our team is mission-driven, high-calibre, and moves fast. Financial services is our domain, and documents are our obsession.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arteria completed its Series B funding round led by Notable Capital (formerly GGV Capital) in October 2023. Other investors include Citi, Illuminate Financial, Information Venture Partners, and BDC Capital. Arteria has received recognition from Gartner (“Cool Vendor” in AI for Banking), CB Insights (Global Top 100 Most Promising FinTechs, 2024, and Global Top 100 Most Promising AI Startups, 2023), and Finovate (Finovate Awards Winner), among others.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Arteria is headquartered in Toronto, with operations in New York and London.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 2&quot;&gt;The Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:280,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:140}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are hiring a Senior Frontend Developer to help build and evolve the web experience at the heart of our platform. You will own significant frontend features end to end, and you will care as much about the problem being solved for the user as the code that solves it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You will build in React and TypeScript, partnering closely with product and design to turn complex business problems into interfaces that feel simple. As one of our senior frontend engineers, you will also help modernize our frontend tooling and&amp;nbsp;practices, and&amp;nbsp;raise the bar for quality across the team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You will set direction on frontend patterns and architecture while staying close to the code: shipping features alongside the team, reviewing pull requests, and collaborating with engineers across the stack. We are a small, focused company, and the decisions you make show up directly in the product.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:160}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
